{
  "stem": "543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, we were in-- we-- we saw open train rails-- train cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no roof on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was middle in January.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just-- so-- how cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you don't know where this was?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it must be past Gliwice, but closer to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They marched us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in those-- in those open trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lillian climbed out of that-- of the thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were shooting at her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't get her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she stole a bread from the SS's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had such a nerve, that one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she went on to the locomotive in-- of-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she get hot our water, and it was warm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we shared it with other people with bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, when I came out of Auschwitz, when we had to go on the march, I had a coat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before I went out, the blockalteste gave me coat before I went out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a warm coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Lillian had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So together, we-- we kept warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With-- between the coat and the blanket, we tried to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were in that open trains, people just froze to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing there-- no food, no heat, no washroom, nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when somebody gets frozen, we just threw 'em out of the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you know, you lose your humanity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes, threw out of the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We get a little bit more place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then, we came on-- in-- in Auschwitz-- in-- in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ravensbruck was a very small concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was mostly for mischlings, they call it-- for people were 1/2, Jewish 1/2, gentile.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
